What we do The 911 Office manages the 9-1-1 System and supports the 10 Public Safety Answering Points throughout the County in their answering of 9-1-1 calls through the procurement of 9-1-1 Telephone Equipment and standardization of call-taking protocols.
Requests for records of 9-1-1 calls and incident information should be made directly to the public safety agency involved in answering the 9-1-1 call and responding to the incident. 9-1-1 calls are answered based on the jurisdiction of where the call originated.
